{"tha-ap30:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap30:0.2":"Subhutivagga ","tha-ap30:0.3":"8 Uttiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap30:1.1":"“Candabhaganaditire, ","tha-ap30:1.2":"susumaro aham tada; ","tha-ap30:1.3":"Sagocarappasutoham, ","tha-ap30:1.4":"naditittham agacchaham. ","tha-ap30:2.1":"Siddhattho tamhi samaye, ","tha-ap30:2.2":"sayambhu aggapuggalo; ","tha-ap30:2.3":"Nadim taritukamo so, ","tha-ap30:2.4":"naditittham upagami. ","tha-ap30:3.1":"Upagate ca sambuddhe, ","tha-ap30:3.2":"ahampi tatthupagamim; ","tha-ap30:3.3":"Upagantvana sambuddham, ","tha-ap30:3.4":"imam vacam udirayim. ","tha-ap30:4.1":"‘Abhiruha mahavira, ","tha-ap30:4.2":"taressami aham tuvam; ","tha-ap30:4.3":"Pettikam visayam mayham, ","tha-ap30:4.4":"anukampa mahamuni’. ","tha-ap30:5.1":"Mama uggajjanam sutva, ","tha-ap30:5.2":"abhiruhi mahamuni; ","tha-ap30:5.3":"Hattho hatthena cittena, ","tha-ap30:5.4":"taresim lokanayakam. ","tha-ap30:6.1":"Nadiya parime tire, ","tha-ap30:6.2":"siddhattho lokanayako; ","tha-ap30:6.3":"Assasesi mamam tattha, ","tha-ap30:6.4":"amatam papunissasi. ","tha-ap30:7.1":"Tamha kaya cavitvana, ","tha-ap30:7.2":"devalokam agacchaham; ","tha-ap30:7.3":"Dibbasukham anubhavim, ","tha-ap30:7.4":"accharahi purakkhato. ","tha-ap30:8.1":"Sattakkhattunca devindo, ","tha-ap30:8.2":"devarajjamakasaham; ","tha-ap30:8.3":"Tinikkhattum cakkavatti, ","tha-ap30:8.4":"mahiya issaro ahum. ","tha-ap30:9.1":"Vivekamanuyuttoham, ","tha-ap30:9.2":"nipako ca susamvuto; ","tha-ap30:9.3":"Dharemi antimam deham, ","tha-ap30:9.4":"sammasambuddhasasane. ","tha-ap30:10.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap30:10.2":"taresim yam narasabham; ","tha-ap30:10.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap30:10.4":"taranaya idam phalam. ","tha-ap30:11.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap30:11.2":"vimokkhapi ca atthime; ","tha-ap30:11.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","tha-ap30:11.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap30:12.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma uttiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap30:13.1":"Uttiyattherassapadanam atthamam. "}